Trevor Noah s highly anticipated autobiographical book, Born A Crime: Stories from a South African Childhood will hit stores worldwide.The scramble for a piece of Noah s life began in September when the comedian welcomed preorder sales on his official website.At the time, the host of The Daily Show also told his SA fans that the book would come with a special cover specifically for them.Consisting of 304 pages of 18 personally written essays, the memoir goes into detail about the comedian s life as a product of a white Swiss father and a black Xhosa mother at a time such unions were illegal in SA.siyabongas@thenewage.co.za